ing: 1/2 cup orange juice, or as needed
des: "This is a lot of fun for kids. I made it up after an afternoon outside with a friend. It's best in summer because there is better fruit."
ins: Place bananas, papaya, pineapple, honeydew, grapes, ice cubes, and yogurt into the bowl of a blender. Pour in orange juice. Cover and puree until smooth, adding additional orange juice if needed to achieve desired consistency.
